    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/3c4fa0638677c9451eb1e92dbc974caf.poster.avif?t=1722845146\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/3c4fa0638677c9451eb1e92dbc974caf.webm?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >&quot;The monsters are the secrets you wish you could forget, but always resurface.&quot;</h2><br>Tako no Himitsu: Ocean of Secrets is an indie Action RPG made as a tribute to the Game Boy Advance era of gaming. A spiritual successor to Save me Mr Tako, play in a world where Octopuses were erased from history.<br><br>Following centuries of peace after the last war between Octopuses and Humans, the world must now face the secrets of its past. Wild animals are slowly disappearing, tensions between countries are brewing following the rise of the mysterious Temple of the Order, and shadow voids are appearing across the lands.<br><br><strong>This demo lets you play two chapters of the game, giving you a taste of the adventure. It features 1.5 hours of gameplay, including battles, puzzles, and a glimpse of the story</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/3f27f44d6c0c8042bf26ddb1d652ee9e.poster.avif?t=1722845146\" width=600 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/3f27f44d6c0c8042bf26ddb1d652ee9e.webm?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/3f27f44d6c0c8042bf26ddb1d652ee9e.mp4?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/7b7958c98c66c44862a81c5c73600ab5.poster.avif?t=1722845146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/7b7958c98c66c44862a81c5c73600ab5.webm?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/7b7958c98c66c44862a81c5c73600ab5.mp4?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Play as six different characters, each with their own unique abilities and Symbiosis power. Discover their individual stories and the traumas they must overcome to make a positive change in the world.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/5b904e26c47c4320140162f8940ff7d7.poster.avif?t=1722845146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/5b904e26c47c4320140162f8940ff7d7.webm?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/5b904e26c47c4320140162f8940ff7d7.mp4?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Befriend and train magical Octopuses, the heroes of the past! Teach them spells that can aid in battle or help solve puzzles whilst exploring the world.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/95e3e6aea52ba5ce412da968307ad1be.poster.avif?t=1722845146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/95e3e6aea52ba5ce412da968307ad1be.webm?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/95e3e6aea52ba5ce412da968307ad1be.mp4?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Strategise in real-time combat and fight the shadow monsters plaguing the land. Swap between different characters to adapt to enemies and gain the upper hand, and keep ahead of the swarm with new equipment.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/a6da03c413c136932eea88f48ddc7506.poster.avif?t=1722845146\" width=600 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/a6da03c413c136932eea88f48ddc7506.webm?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3068030/extras/a6da03c413c136932eea88f48ddc7506.mp4?t=1722845146\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore a vast, troubled world and learn the secrets of its past as you travel across the land. Discover the truth of the Shadow War and meet memorable characters in a great adventure to restore light to the world.</li></ul>",
